      <p>For more on harm reduction and nicotine alternatives, read the <a href="https://www.rcp.ac.uk/improving-care/resources/nicotine-without-smoke-tobacco-harm-reduction/">Royal College of Physicians' research on nicotine without smoke</a>, a foundational resource for understanding harm reduction.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Shop>
